# 🔐 Phishing URL Detection System

A Machine Learning-based web application that detects whether a given URL is **phishing** or **legitimate** using feature extraction and trained models.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

This project is designed to enhance cybersecurity by identifying malicious URLs using machine learning techniques. It extracts multiple features from a URL and predicts whether it is safe or not.

---

## 🧠 Key Features

- 🔍 URL Analysis using feature extraction  
- 🤖 Machine Learning model for prediction  
- 🌐 Web interface using Flask  
- ⚡ Fast and real-time detection  
- 📊 Uses PCA for dimensionality reduction  
- 💾 Pre-trained model integration  

---

# 🛡️ Phishing URL Detector

A Machine Learning tool to classify URLs as legitimate or phishing.

## 🧰 Tech Stack

Python · Scikit-learn · Pandas · NumPy  

## ✨ Features

- Feature engineering: URL length, special characters, domain age  
- High-precision classification model  
- Clean data pipeline from raw URLs to predictions  

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python detector.py
